# Build context trimming for dev/Dockerfile (context = repo root). Deps are installed inside the
# image, so host node_modules/build output/local state are excluded. `.dev.vars` is intentionally
# KEPT — the containers need local secrets to run (dev only).
**/node_modules
.git
**/dist
**/.wrangler
**/.vite
**/.output
**/.turbo
*.log
.DS_Store
